.TH HYPRLAND\-UPDATE\-SCREEN 1 "2025-11-20" "hyprland-guiutils 0.2.1" "Hyprland Ecosystem"
.SH NAME
hyprland\-update\-screen \- display Hyprland update notification
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hyprland\-update\-screen
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hyprland\-update\-screen
is a GUI notification screen displayed after Hyprland has been updated.
It informs users about the update and provides links to release notes
and the Hyprland news page.
.PP
This utility is invoked automatically by Hyprland after an update and is
not typically run directly by users.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-\-new\-version " string"
The new version string to display in the notification title.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR Hyprland (1)
.SH AUTHOR
The Hyprland Development Team
.SH BUGS
Report bugs at
.UR https://github.com/hyprwm/hyprland-guiutils/issues
.UE .
